flowchart LR
    Client[Client Request<br/>POST /users or PUT /users/:id] --> Router[HTTP Router / Handler]
    Router --> Validator[Request Validation]
    Validator --> Service[User Service]

    Service --> Cache[Cache Layer<br/>optional read-through cache]
    Service --> Repo[Repository Interface]
    Repo --> DB[(Database Layer)]
    DB --> PG[(PostgreSQL)]

    Service --> Publisher[Event Publisher Interface]
    Publisher --> MQ[(Message Queue<br/>RabbitMQ / broker abstraction)]
    MQ --> Notifier[Notification Service]
    Notifier --> Notify[Send Notification<br/>welcome email / update alert]

    subgraph Observability[Observability]
        Logger[Structured Logging]
        Metrics[Metrics + Health Checks]
    end

    Service --> Logger
    Service --> Metrics

    DB -. persisted data .-> DataModel[User record<br/>id, email, name, status, created_at, updated_at]
    MQ -. async event .-> EventMsg[Event payload<br/>user.created / user.updated<br/>user_id, email, event_type]

    subgraph RequestData[Request Data]
        ReqData[Create / Update payload<br/>name, email, status]
    end

    Validator --> ReqData
    ReqData --> Service

    PG -->|response| Service
    Notifier -->|async side effect| Service
    Service -->|response| Client
